¿En serio?

00:19:35.490 --> 00:19:38.850
...Aaaaaaa uuuuuuuuuu aaaaaaaaaa...

00:19:37.920 --> 00:19:41.030
¿Qué hay de mi estrellaaaaaaaaaaaa?

00:19:39.700 --> 00:19:40.740
...Estrellaaaaaaaa.....

00:19:41.040 --> 00:19:45.000
¿Qué hay de mi estrellaaaaaaaaaaa?

00:19:42.780 --> 00:19:50.430
Estrellaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa...

00:19:45.070 --> 00:19:50.410
¿Qué hay de mi estrella?

00:19:50.230 --> 00:19:51.330
Ranka...

00:19:50.410 --> 00:19:54.950
Guoooooooooooo ouuuuu...

00:19:52.990 --> 00:19:54.100
Sheryl...

